# CI/CD Practice Project

A Python project demonstrating a full CI/CD pipeline using GitHub Actions.

## Pipeline Features
- ✅ Automated testing with pytest on every push
- ✅ Code style enforcement with flake8
- ✅ Runs on Ubuntu (cloud) automatically

## How it works
Every time code is pushed to `main`, GitHub Actions automatically:
1. Sets up Python 3.11
2. Installs dependencies
3. Runs the linter (flake8)
4. Runs all tests (pytest)